    props: { title: "Crypto Custody Insurance: Protecting Your Digital Assets", categoryName: "Crypto Insurance", categorySlug: "insurance", readTime: "8 min", intro: "Crypto custody insurance protects against the loss of digital assets held by exchanges, custodians, and institutional storage providers. Unlike traditional bank deposits protected by FDIC insurance, crypto assets require specialized coverage. This guide explains how custody insurance works, what it covers, and how to evaluate whether your assets are adequately protected." },
    toc: [],
